Pick up the cell phone from the front left corner of the table.
Move a step to the right so you're a bit closer to the laptop while still holding the cell phone.
Place the phone in the clear bowl on the table.

Turn and move to the television while carrying the bowl.
Place the bowl with the phone in it on the left edge of the television stand.
